overview: Mark this hot little number down as "Surprise, surprise, surprise." Jackrabbit Releasing concludes it's "Seasons of Sex" quartet - the other three being Spring Fling, Summer Shooters, and the kick-ass Fall Ballers - with this really rockin' entry. Cover model Pete Ross appears in two really well-done scenes, and Brad Star is paired with the almost unbearably cute Latino hottie Hawk Munez. Their tryst started off rather mildly but picked up quickly, ending with a thick facial cumshot and some yummy post-spewing licking.
title: Winter Wood
